long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: GPT Chat Logger is an extension which lets you save your active conversation in Chat GPT to a text file locally on your computer. All you have to do is click an active conversation, click the store icon, and then save the file to your computer. These steps can also be seen in the photos.
